router-id 0.0.0.2
network 2.0.0.0 0.255.255.255 area 0
network 192.1.12.0 0.0.0.255 area 0
network 192.1.23.0 0.0.0.255 area 0

r3
outer ospf 1
router-id 0.0.0.3
